headline: Q3 Rundown: Rollins (NYSE:ROL) Vs Other Environmental and Facilities Services Stocks
summary: As the Q3 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the environmental and facilities services industry, including Rollins (NYSE:ROL) and its peers.
